## Post 1

**Date:** 3 July 2026

**Topic:** Why YouTube matters for AI visibility

### Summary
Ross shares research showing that Google's AI (Gemini) cites YouTube significantly more often than Instagram or TikTok. He argues that YouTube Shorts are becoming an essential distribution channel for B2B software companies because AI search increasingly references video content. As AI-powered search evolves, brands that invest in YouTube are more likely to gain visibility in AI-generated responses.

### Main Takeaway
YouTube is becoming a critical channel for AI visibility, making short-form video an essential part of modern B2B content strategy.

